list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: 1.calibration position A1 is renamed to A0. This allows the first row of samples to start from A1 2. New versions of slide labware tailored to 4.3. software update are introduced. Please download them and replace in the OT2 app (by deleting the existing files and adding new ones – using remove-add dialogue of the app) 3. sample_z_correction_factor is introduced. Use it in case the adjustment to z-position of tip over the sample is needed.

Edits as per Derek Oldridge's suggestions
Edits as per Derek Oldridge's suggestions

Updated the IMC protocol to introduce an option of a manual pause and a 4C overnight incubation. Merged the CODEX_single_stain and CODEX_multicycle protocols into one protocol and added the options for FFPE and Antibody_Screening modes in the *MODIFIABLE RUN PARAMETER* section. Setting Antibody_Screening to False makes this protocol run like CODEX_multicycle, setting it to true makes it run like CODEX_single_stain

Please download them and replace in the OT2 app (by deleting the existing files and adding new ones – using remove-add dialogue of the app) 3. sample_z_correction_factor is introduced. Use it in case the adjustment to z-position of tip over the sample is needed.
